Read: `coding-playbook/foundations/conventions`, `coding-playbook/architecture/module-patterns`

- [x] 5a. Create `src/lib/shiki/theme/aideTheme.json` -- TextMate-format Shiki theme. Colors: background `#0a0906`, foreground `#e8dfce`. Token rules: `keyword.*`, `storage.*`, `constant.language` → `#3d6b4a`; `string.*`, `punctuation.definition.string` → `#d6b25a`; `variable.*`, `entity.name.function`, `support.function` → `#e8dfce`; `comment.*`, `punctuation.definition.comment` → `rgba(232,223,206,0.55)`; `punctuation.*` (non-string) → `rgba(232,223,206,0.55)`; `entity.name.tag`, `markup.heading` → `#3d6b4a`. Name it `aide-theme`.
