- [x] 9e. Create `src/components/Expo/index.tsx` -- client orchestrator. Reads `useExpoTip()`; resolves tip from EXPO_TIPS[activeSection]. Fixed `position: fixed; bottom: 24px; right: 24px; z-index: 20; pointer-events: none;`. Renders ExpoSpeechBubble (pointer-events: auto) when !dismissed + sprite `<img src="/expo-{pose}.png" width={140}>` wrapped in pointer-events-auto button that re-opens the bubble when dismissed. Float animation via `expoFloat` keyframe (in globals.css from step 1d): 4s ease-in-out infinite, translate-y-[-6px] + rotate(1deg) at 50%.
- [x] 9f. Wrap the root layout's `<body>` children in `<ExpoTipProvider>` (edit step 1e's layout.tsx).
